<h2>Reset Your Password</h2>

<p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>

<p>We received a request to reset the password for your Immobilier.ch account. If you made this request, click the button below to create a new password.</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
  <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="btn-primary">Reset Password</a>
</div>

<div class="warning-box">
  <p><strong>This link will expire in {{expiresIn}}.</strong></p>
</div>

<p><strong>Didn't request this?</strong></p>
<p>If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged and your account is secure.</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <p>For your security, we recommend never sharing your password with anyone and using a unique, strong password for your account.</p>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #757575;">
  If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
  <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="word-break: break-all;">{{resetUrl}}</a>
</p>

<p>Best regards,<br><strong>The Immobilier.ch Team</strong></p>
